title: Club Dance Mix 1
description:
And here is a Dance mix I made with VirtualDJ. Feel free to comment, hints and tips are welcome.

2.	Rihanna - Don't Stop The Music (The Wideboys Club Mix)
3.	Kleerup ft. Robyn - With Every Heartbeat (Wonderland Remix)
4.	Dubfire - Roadkill (Cedric Gervais Remix)
5.	Just in Timberlake - Love Stoned (Don Zee Remix)
6.	Booty Luv - Boogie 2nite (Seamus Haji Big Love Remix)
7.	Axwell ft. Steve Edwards - Watch the Sunrise (Bob Sinclair Remix)

9.	Axwell - I Found You (Axwells Remode)

Hope you enjoy it...
